    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <note>The following subdivision and the incipits of the text parts are taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="BLorient12034"/>, 
                    quoted according to the catalogue description in 
                    <bibl><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary"/><citedRange unit="page">148</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Haemor" xml:lang="am">
                    <label>Prescription against haemorrhoids</label>
                    <note>Indicated as "prescription against haemorrhoids" by 
                        <bibl><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary"/><citedRange unit="page">148</citedRange></bibl>. 
                        However, <foreign xml:lang="am">ለጀርባ፡ ደዌ፡</foreign> and <foreign xml:lang="am">ጀርባው፡</foreign> in the incipit may 
                        also refer to 'back pain' (<foreign xml:lang="am">ጀርባ፡</foreign> 'back'), while <foreign xml:lang="am">ለወጣ፡</foreign> 
                        could be related to <foreign xml:lang="am">ዋጣ፡</foreign> 'scabies'
                        (cf. <bibl><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1968Medecine"/><citedRange unit="page">111</citedRange></bibl>).</note>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ለጀርባ፡ ደዌ፡ ጀርባው፡ ለወጣ፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Ears" xml:lang="gez">
                    <label>Prescription against disease of the ears</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ለሕማመ፡ ዕዝን፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Eti" xml:lang="am">
                    <label>Prescription against ʾǝṭi</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ለዕጢ፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Impotence" xml:lang="gez">
                    <label>Prescription against impotence</label>
                    <note>For other prescriptions related to <foreign xml:lang="gez">እስኪት፡</foreign> 'penis', cf.
                        <bibl><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1968Medecine"/><citedRange unit="page">87</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ለዘሞተ፡ እስኪቱ፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Goods" xml:lang="gez">
                    <label>Prescription to find no goods</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>ወትረክብ፡ ዓቢየ፡ ንዋየ፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="textsubunit" xml:id="Colic" xml:lang="am">
                    <label>Prescription against colic</label>
                    <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                        <ab>የቁርፀት፡</ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
